-Goupitan.pdf|publisher=Chinese National Committee on Large Dams|accessdate=2010-03-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416183422/http://www.chincold.org.cn/news/li080321-16-Goupitan.pdf|archivedate=2014-04-16|df=}}</ref><ref>[http://news.163.com/06/0830/00/2PO1FN8J0001rt.html 构皮滩水电站工程情况简介_网易新闻中心<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.gz.xinhuanet.com/zfpd/2007-08/20/content_10907676.htm 四在农家――余庆<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
