The '''Mărișelu Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Cluj County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 100 individual [[wind turbine]]s,<ref>[http://www.ziuadecj.ro/action/article?ID=3758 Cea mai mare ferma eoliana va fi construita in Judetul Cluj {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 3 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 300 MW of power, enough to power over 180,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$230 million.

